{"arkId":"cl010113569","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010113569","modified ":"2026-03-11","title":"Coupe balustre","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Coupe balustre"}],"displayDateCreated":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1667","currentLocation":"non expos\u00e9","room":"","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1667,"endYear":"","imprecision":"","text":"3e quart du XVIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Lockeman, Nicolaes","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"Orf\u00e8vre","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"CL 20523","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"orf\u00e8vrerie, argenterie ; coupe","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Coupe de forme cylindrique couverte. La base circulaire, le pied \u00e0 balustre, la partie basse et renfl\u00e9e de la coupe et le couvercle sont orn\u00e9s de feuilles de ch\u00eane encadrant d\u0027autres fleurs \u00e9maill\u00e9es plus petites en blanc, noir et vert. La plus grande partie de la coupe est couverte d\u0027un bandeau \u00e9maill\u00e9 repr\u00e9sentant diff\u00e9rents \u00e9pisodes de la bataille navale livr\u00e9e par les Hollandais contre les Anglais en juin 1667. A l\u0027int\u00e9rieur du couvercle, une inscription en n\u00e9erlandais r\u00e9sume l\u0027\u00e9pisode. Cette coupe fut offerte \u00e0 Corneille de Witt apr\u00e8s la victoire n\u00e9erlandaise de la Medway (9-14 juin 1667)","inscriptions":"Inscription : \r ; Armoiries de la Province de Hollande, \u00e9cu surmont\u00e9 d\u0027une couronne ducale : sur le couvercle\r ; Inscription en hollandais (voir photo) indiquant que la coupe est un cadeau des Etats des Provinces-Unies \u00e0 Corneille de Witt en comm\u00e9moration des combats des 21, 22, 23 juin \u00e0 l\u0027embouchure de la Tamise. (A l\u0027int\u00e9rieur du couvercle)\r ; Poin\u00e7on : \r ; C ou O ou Q ? sur le bord int\u00e9rieur du couvercle.","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"30","displayDimension":"30 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Diam\u00e8tre","value":"15","displayDimension":"15 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Diam\u00e8tre","value":"12","displayDimension":"12 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : or (\u00e9maill\u00e9)\r\nTechnique : techniques m\u00e9tal (orf\u00e8vrerie)","placeOfCreation":"La Haye (Europe-\u003EPays-Bas = Pays Bas = Hollande)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Offerte \u00e0 Corneille de Witt le 7 novembre 1667 ; ses descendants jusqu\u0027au XIX\u00e8 si\u00e8cle. Collection de Mayer Karl von Rothschild (1820-1886) \u00e0 Francfort ; Collection de Ad\u00e8le von Rothschild (1843-1922), baronne Salomon de Rothschild ; legs, 1922","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"Rothschild, Baronne Salomon de, n\u00e9e Ad\u00e8le de Rothschild","note":"","role":", Donateur"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"legs","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date d\u0027arriv\u00e9e au Mus\u00e9e","value":"1922","startYear":1922,"endYear":1922}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e national du Moyen-\u00c2ge - mus\u00e9e de Cluny, Paris","longTermLoanTo":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","index":{"Mode d\u0027acquisition":[{"value":"legs"}],"place":[{"value":"La Haye"}],"objectType":[{"value"